2. EpubSanitizer (https://github.com/qinlili23333/EpubSanitizer)
   - License: AGPL-3.0 or Qinlili Universal License
   - Inspiration: EPUB 3.0 standardization and sanitization concepts

3. calibre (https://github.com/kovidgoyal/calibre)
   - License: GPL-3.0
   - Inspiration: E-book format conversion functionality

We thank the authors of these projects for their excellent work and contributions
to the open-source community.

